      },
      {
        "type": "article",
        "id": "BJNR039300021BJNE000300000",
        "name": "\u00a7 2",
        "title": "Abrechnung des Finanzausgleichs unter den L\u00e4ndern im Ausgleichsjahr 2017",
        "parent": null,
        "body": "<P>F\u00fcr das Ausgleichsjahr 2017 wird der Finanzausgleich unter den L\u00e4ndern wie folgt festgestellt: <DL Type=\"arabic\"><DT>1.</DT><DD Font=\"normal\"><LA>endg\u00fcltige Ausgleichsbeitr\u00e4ge: <table colsep=\"0\" frame=\"none\" pgwide=\"0\" rowsep=\"0\" tabstyle=\"finanz\" tocentry=\"%yes;\"><tgroup align=\"left\" char=\"\" charoff=\"50\" cols=\"2\"><colspec colname=\"col1\" colwidth=\"45*\" /><colspec colname=\"col2\" colwidth=\"35*\" /><tbody valign=\"top\"><row><entry VJ=\"1\" align=\"justify\" colname=\"col1\">von Baden-W\u00fcrttemberg</entry><entry VJ=\"1\" align=\"right\" colname=\"col2\">2\u00a0763\u00a0396\u00a0453,98 Euro</entry></row><row><entry VJ=\"1\" align=\"justify\" colname=\"col1\">von Bayern</entry><entry VJ=\"1\" align=\"right\" colname=\"col2\">5\u00a0865\u00a0769\u00a0672,92 Euro</entry></row><row><entry VJ=\"1\" align=\"justify\" colname=\"col1\">von Hamburg</entry><entry VJ=\"1\" align=\"right\" colname=\"col2\">35\u00a0179\u00a0662,75 Euro</entry></row><row><entry VJ=\"1\" align=\"justify\" colname=\"col1\">von Hessen</entry><entry VJ=\"1\" align=\"right\" colname=\"col2\">2\u00a0475\u00a0299\u00a0995,35 Euro,</entry></row></tbody></tgroup></table></LA></DD><DT>2.</DT><DD Font=\"normal\"><LA>endg\u00fcltige Ausgleichszuweisungen: <table colsep=\"0\" frame=\"none\" pgwide=\"0\" rowsep=\"0\" tabstyle=\"finanz\" tocentry=\"%yes;\"><tgroup align=\"left\" char=\"\" charoff=\"50\" cols=\"2\"><colspec colname=\"col1\" colwidth=\"41*\" /><colspec colname=\"col2\" colwidth=\"32*\" /><tbody valign=\"top\"><row><entry VJ=\"1\" align=\"justify\" colname=\"col1\">an Berlin</entry><entry VJ=\"1\" align=\"right\" colname=\"col2\">4\u00a0234\u00a0831\u00a0989,37 Euro</entry></row><row><entry VJ=\"1\" align=\"justify\" colname=\"col1\">an Brandenburg</entry><entry VJ=\"1\" align=\"right\" colname=\"col2\">604\u00a0475\u00a0661,50 Euro</entry></row><row><entry VJ=\"1\" align=\"justify\" colname=\"col1\">an Bremen</entry><entry VJ=\"1\" align=\"right\" colname=\"col2\">689\u00a0125\u00a0512,48 Euro</entry></row><row><entry VJ=\"1\" align=\"justify\" colname=\"col1\">an\u00a0Mecklenburg-Vorpommern</entry><entry VJ=\"1\" align=\"right\" colname=\"col2\">519\u00a0899\u00a0091,10 Euro</entry></row><row><entry VJ=\"1\" align=\"justify\" colname=\"col1\">an Niedersachsen</entry><entry VJ=\"1\" align=\"right\" colname=\"col2\">696\u00a0419\u00a0450,39 Euro</entry></row><row><entry VJ=\"1\" align=\"justify\" colname=\"col1\">an Nordrhein-Westfalen</entry><entry VJ=\"1\" align=\"right\" colname=\"col2\">1\u00a0226\u00a0689\u00a0661,88 Euro</entry></row><row><entry VJ=\"1\" align=\"justify\" colname=\"col1\">an Rheinland-Pfalz</entry><entry VJ=\"1\" align=\"right\" colname=\"col2\">390\u00a0227\u00a0646,52 Euro</entry></row><row><entry VJ=\"1\" align=\"justify\" colname=\"col1\">an das Saarland</entry><entry VJ=\"1\" align=\"right\" colname=\"col2\">196\u00a0427\u00a0246,22 Euro</entry></row><row><entry VJ=\"1\" align=\"justify\" colname=\"col1\">an Sachsen</entry><entry VJ=\"1\" align=\"right\" colname=\"col2\">1\u00a0174\u00a0976\u00a0327,94 Euro</entry></row><row><entry VJ=\"1\" align=\"justify\" colname=\"col1\">an Sachsen-Anhalt</entry><entry VJ=\"1\" align=\"right\" colname=\"col2\">533\u00a0342\u00a0563,19 Euro</entry></row><row><entry VJ=\"1\" align=\"justify\" colname=\"col1\">an Schleswig-Holstein</entry><entry VJ=\"1\" align=\"right\" colname=\"col2\">238\u00a0129\u00a0419,93 Euro</entry></row><row><entry VJ=\"1\" align=\"justify\" colname=\"col1\">an Th\u00fcringen</entry><entry VJ=\"1\" align=\"right\" colname=\"col2\">635\u00a0101\u00a0214,49 Euro.</entry></row></tbody></tgroup></table></LA></DD></DL></P>",
        "footnotes": null,
        "documentaryFootnotes": null
      },
      {
        "type": "article",
        "id": "BJNR039300021BJNE000400000",
        "name": "\u00a7 3",
        "title": "Abschlusszahlungen f\u00fcr 2017",
        "parent": null,
        "body": "<P>Zum Ausgleich der Unterschiede zwischen den vorl\u00e4ufig gezahlten und den endg\u00fcltig festgestellten L\u00e4nderanteilen an der Umsatzsteuer nach \u00a7 1, den vorl\u00e4ufig gezahlten und den endg\u00fcltig festgestellten Ausgleichsbeitr\u00e4gen und Ausgleichszuweisungen nach \u00a7 2 werden nach \u00a7 15 des Finanzausgleichsgesetzes mit dem Inkrafttreten dieser Verordnung f\u00e4llig: <DL Type=\"arabic\"><DT>1.</DT><DD Font=\"normal\"><LA>\u00dcberweisungen von zahlungspflichtigen L\u00e4ndern: <table colsep=\"0\" frame=\"none\" pgwide=\"0\" rowsep=\"0\" tabstyle=\"finanz\" tocentry=\"%yes;\"><tgroup align=\"left\" char=\"\" charoff=\"50\" cols=\"2\"><colspec colname=\"col1\" colwidth=\"51*\" /><colspec colname=\"col2\" colwidth=\"32*\" /><tbody valign=\"top\"><row><entry VJ=\"1\" align=\"justify\" colname=\"col1\">von Brandenburg</entry><entry VJ=\"1\" align=\"right\" colname=\"col2\">192\u00a0820,47 Euro</entry></row><row><entry VJ=\"1\" align=\"justify\" colname=\"col1\">von Bremen</entry><entry VJ=\"1\" align=\"right\" colname=\"col2\">6\u00a0178\u00a0795,01 Euro</entry></row><row><entry VJ=\"1\" align=\"justify\" colname=\"col1\">von Mecklenburg-Vorpommern</entry><entry VJ=\"1\" align=\"right\" colname=\"col2\">3\u00a0554\u00a0495,28 Euro</entry></row><row><entry VJ=\"1\" align=\"justify\" colname=\"col1\">von Nordrhein-Westfalen</entry><entry VJ=\"1\" align=\"right\" colname=\"col2\">51\u00a0999\u00a0892,26 Euro</entry></row><row><entry VJ=\"1\" align=\"justify\" colname=\"col1\">von Rheinland-Pfalz</entry><entry VJ=\"1\" align=\"right\" colname=\"col2\">3\u00a0583\u00a0945,65 Euro</entry></row><row><entry VJ=\"1\" align=\"justify\" colname=\"col1\">von dem Saarland</entry><entry VJ=\"1\" align=\"right\" colname=\"col2\">6\u00a0264\u00a0057,18 Euro</entry></row><row><entry VJ=\"1\" align=\"justify\" colname=\"col1\">von Sachsen</entry><entry VJ=\"1\" align=\"right\" colname=\"col2\">23\u00a0328\u00a0460,78 Euro</entry></row><row><entry VJ=\"1\" align=\"justify\" colname=\"col1\">von Sachsen-Anhalt</entry><entry VJ=\"1\" align=\"right\" colname=\"col2\">19\u00a0297\u00a0288,75 Euro</entry></row><row><entry VJ=\"1\" align=\"justify\" colname=\"col1\">von Schleswig-Holstein</entry><entry VJ=\"1\" align=\"right\" colname=\"col2\">207\u00a0641,86 Euro</entry></row><row><entry VJ=\"1\" align=\"justify\" colname=\"col1\">von Th\u00fcringen</entry><entry VJ=\"1\" align=\"right\" colname=\"col2\">14\u00a0747\u00a0889,14 Euro,</entry></row></tbody></tgroup></table></LA></DD><DT>2.</DT><DD Font=\"normal\"><LA>Zahlungen an empfangsberechtigte L\u00e4nder: <table colsep=\"0\" frame=\"none\" pgwide=\"0\" rowsep=\"0\" tabstyle=\"finanz2\" tocentry=\"%yes;\"><tgroup align=\"left\" char=\"\" charoff=\"50\" cols=\"2\"><colspec colname=\"col1\" colwidth=\"45*\" /><colspec colname=\"col2\" colwidth=\"35*\" /><tbody valign=\"top\"><row><entry VJ=\"1\" align=\"justify\" colname=\"col1\">an Baden-W\u00fcrttemberg</entry><entry VJ=\"1\" align=\"right\" colname=\"col2\">31\u00a0187\u00a0635,12 Euro</entry></row><row><entry VJ=\"1\" align=\"justify\" colname=\"col1\">an Bayern</entry><entry VJ=\"1\" align=\"right\" colname=\"col2\">39\u00a0604\u00a0981,23 Euro</entry></row><row><entry VJ=\"1\" align=\"justify\" colname=\"col1\">an Berlin</entry><entry VJ=\"1\" align=\"right\" colname=\"col2\">16\u00a0805\u00a0248,51 Euro</entry></row><row><entry VJ=\"1\" align=\"justify\" colname=\"col1\">an Hamburg</entry><entry VJ=\"1\" align=\"right\" colname=\"col2\">8\u00a0233\u00a0920,84 Euro</entry></row><row><entry VJ=\"1\" align=\"justify\" colname=\"col1\">an Hessen</entry><entry VJ=\"1\" align=\"right\" colname=\"col2\">11\u00a0438\u00a0452,93 Euro</entry></row><row><entry VJ=\"1\" align=\"justify\" colname=\"col1\">an Niedersachsen</entry><entry VJ=\"1\" align=\"right\" colname=\"col2\">22\u00a0085\u00a0047,76 Euro.</entry></row></tbody></tgroup></table></LA></DD></DL></P>",
        "footnotes": null,
        "documentaryFootnotes": null
      },
      {
        "type": "article",
        "id": "BJNR039300021BJNE000500000",
        "name": "\u00a7 4",
        "title": "Inkrafttreten, Au\u00dferkrafttreten",
        "parent": null,
        "body": "<P>Diese Verordnung tritt am siebenten Tag nach der Verk\u00fcndung in Kraft. Gleichzeitig tritt die Erste Verordnung zur Durchf\u00fchrung des Finanzausgleichsgesetzes im Ausgleichsjahr 2017 vom 31. M\u00e4rz 2017 (BGBl. I S. 689) au\u00dfer Kraft.</P>",
        "footnotes": null,
        "documentaryFootnotes": null
      }
    ]
  }
}
